You can use your tracking number at www.USPS.com in the Quick Tools Tracking section. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Duplicate Notice Was Mailed
body: On June 24, 2021, we sent you a duplicate notice about a decision on your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190147974, or describing how we will process the case if it is still pending. Your case is located at our Potomac Service Center location. Please follow any instructions in the notice. If you do not receive your duplicate notice by July 24, 2021, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request a copy of the notice. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Request for Initial Evidence Was Sent
body: On June 11, 2021, we sent a request for initial evidence for your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190147975. The request for evidence explains what we need from you. We will not take action on your case until we receive the evidence or the deadline to submit it expires. Please follow the instructions in the request for evidence. If you do not receive your request for evidence by June 26, 2021, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request a copy of the notice. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
